https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qo3AFzu8WS0k87GdXtoErrkV8Ad.jpg Anthony Fonseca, nicknamed "Cymbaline", enjoys a hobby of photography and graffiti, which he practices together with his friend Fanny. Suddenly, two girls reappear in his life: Michelle, an editor of a magazine and social climber, and Flavia, a very rich daughter of a bored and spoiled father. Anthony thus finds himself having to share his life with three girls who are completely different from each other, but at a certain point he realizes that he is being followed by a fourth woman, a mysterious and unknown girl.
